gov.nasa.larcfm.Util

Class Matrix2d

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.larcfm.Util.Matrix2d

  • public class Matrix2d
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a basic (and naive) implementation of an MxN matrix of doubles, with associated functions.
